{"seq":103,"t":1784385355229,"type":"hypothesis","version":1,"narration":"This is classic Sokoban — the Player walks, is blocked by Walls, pushes single Crates into empty cells, and ACTION does nothing.","code":"title Sokoban Clone\nauthor GLASSBOX\n\n========\nOBJECTS\n========\n\nBackground\nlightgray\n\nWall\ndarkgray\n\nPlayer\nblue\n\nCrate\norange\n\nTarget\nred\n\n=======\nLEGEND\n=======\n\n@ = Crate and Target\n# = Wall\nP = Player\n* = Crate\nO = Target\n\n=======\nSOUNDS\n=======\n\n================\nCOLLISIONLAYERS\n================\n\nBackground\nTarget\nPlayer, Wall, Crate\n\n======\nRULES\n======\n\n[ > Player | Crate ] -> [ > Player | > Crate ]\n\n==============\nWINCONDITIONS\n==============\n\nAll Crate on Target\n\n=======\nLEVELS\n=======\n\n####..\n#.O#..\n#..###\n#@P..#\n#..*.#\n#..###\n####.."}
