{"seq":148,"t":1784385377085,"type":"converged","version":2,"episodes":12,"totalSteps":98,"discoveries":["Player+Target and Crate+Target share cells, but Player and Crate never do, so Target lives on its own collision layer while Player/Crate/Wall share one.","Pushing works: A1 DOWN moves Player onto the crate's old cell while the crate slides one down, confirming a single push rule.","Walls block: A2 LEFT (into a wall) and A6 repeated DOWN into a wall leave the grid unchanged.","The Crate+Target cell stays fixed and the player can occupy a Target (A7 shows Player+Target), so Target is a passive overlay object.","No logged attempt wins; two crates and two targets (one already satisfied) suggest \"All Crate on Target\" as the win condition.","The prior crash was purely a missing \".\" = Background legend entry, not a logic error."],"planLen":33,"realOptimal":33}
{"seq":149,"t":1784385377086,"type":"run_end","converged":true,"versions":2,"episodes":12,"totalSteps":98,"discoveries":["Player+Target and Crate+Target share cells, but Player and Crate never do, so Target lives on its own collision layer while Player/Crate/Wall share one.","Pushing works: A1 DOWN moves Player onto the crate's old cell while the crate slides one down, confirming a single push rule.","Walls block: A2 LEFT (into a wall) and A6 repeated DOWN into a wall leave the grid unchanged.","The Crate+Target cell stays fixed and the player can occupy a Target (A7 shows Player+Target), so Target is a passive overlay object.","No logged attempt wins; two crates and two targets (one already satisfied) suggest \"All Crate on Target\" as the win condition.","The prior crash was purely a missing \".\" = Background legend entry, not a logic error."],"planLen":33,"planStates":588,"realOptimal":33}
